            <div id="dsq-comment-message-126" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>hmmm, i&#8217;d say invest in some risers and put 4 gpus on one board.  You can get risers for X16 or X1 slots.  If you do get risers for X1 slots, make sure they are powered or you&#8217;ll blow a hole in the mobo.  That would shave down 100W per mobo eliminated.  So remove 7 mobos and that would save 700W maybe.</p>
